phase2.explanation:
The `/` route matches everything, so other routes are never reached.

**The fix:**
```go
http.HandleFunc("/", func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {
    if r.URL.Path != "/" {
        http.NotFound(w, r)
        return
    }
    fmt.Fprintf(w, "Hello")
})
```

**Go-chan says:**
"`/` matches everything. Handle 404 for other paths."

